title: Fires of Industry
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While on a [[plane]] with this property, a creature has [[advantage]] when using an artisan's [[toolset]] (such as baking with [[cook's utensils]], or forging an item with [[smith's tools]]) when it incorporates flame of this plane into its craft in place of mundane flame.